column5: If this is a duplicate post, please excuse! I just read the  Canadian Ice fishing Expo is Dec. 14,15, 2019 and has moved to Georgian College this year. It was a good event last year and this is their 3rd one.
Yes Mr.B. Moved to the college. Free parking still, so I have been told.
Have to try and make it for a morning entertainment.
Never attended before, any deals to be had on ice huts?
also interested in mainly ice huts ....!!!
Previous years, there may have been 1 or 2 , but not a bunch of them. Not sure why .
There were a few last year and I expect that there will be more this year as there will be more vendors! See you there!
